{
  "stem": "22660.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got more familiar with the SS and the SA, as well as they had a newspaper called which was a Nazi newspaper that made caricatures out of Jewish people, with very ugly names, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But our life went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went to school, our life went on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] business really was not any worse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, my father didn't notice business-wise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We lived, as I said, in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Hamburg was a very international, large city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think people in smaller towns in the southern part of Germany probably noticed it quicker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But my parents, as I said, for four generations lived in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My grandfather's second cousin was Max Warburg, the very famous banker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so that-- we just sort of really pushed it away, and didn't pay much attention to it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because in reality, they just never thought, no matter what Hitler would do, it would pass.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It wouldn't stay that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and if it didn't pass, it wouldn't really attack them, not them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were who they were, and they just felt they would not be touched.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so time went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it got-- the news was worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, you would hear on the news bad things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember some people started leaving to the United States, or other parts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But my parents didn't budge at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember as late as 1938, maybe the spring of 1938, when the movement was much, much stronger by that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were at '33, so that was five years later.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
